headline: Broadcom (AVGO) Draws Investor Interest Amid AI Growth Expectations
summary: Broadcom Inc. (NASDAQ:AVGO) is one of Goldman Sachs’s top growth stock picks. On February 17, Cathie Wood’s ARK ETF disclosed that it acquired 24,205 shares of Broadcom Inc.
